<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>121</hymn_number>
<author>J.R. Ahle</author>
<title>Ry Jesosy, ampombay FFPM121</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ry Jesosy, ampombay
 Fiadanana maharo
 Fo sy saina izahay,
 Ka mba ampahafantaro,
 Raha ny holatrao jerena,
 Fa Anao ny fandresena !

[V2]
 Ry Mpandresy, ambarao
 Aminay ny vokatr'ady :
 Famonjena, aim-baovao
 No andramany sahady :
 Raha ny tafika miseho,
 Fiadanam-po omeo !</lyrics>
</song>